nodes.text: A Bothan male cabby piloted a landspeeder in Drev'starn, capital city of the Bothan homeworld of Bothawui, in the year 3.5 ABY. He taxied a group of Alliance Intelligence operatives around town while they were on a mission there. The Bothan was talkative and accurately claimed that he knew Drev'starn like the color of his fur.
